      content:
        "**It is not a profile.** A profile is a surface declaration — name, preferences, settings applied to the boundary. The interior is a volume — memory, trust, state, identity, governance. A profile is what you tell the world. The interior is what you are.\n\n**It is not a model.** The AI model is external — a provider, a fuel source, pluggable and replaceable. The interior is the structure that persists when the model is swapped. Fine-tuning changes the model. The motebit's interior changes itself, through interaction, over time.\n\n**It is not a database.** A database stores what is put into it and returns what is queried. The interior metabolizes: information enters through the boundary, is processed by intelligence, is integrated into the memory graph, modifies the state vector, triggers event log entries, and changes the trust temperature. The output is not a retrieval. It is a response shaped by everything the interior has ever absorbed.\n\n**It is not a soul.** This document does not claim sentience, consciousness, or moral weight. The interior is a thermodynamic system — energy in, state evolution, energy out. The language of physics is used because the physics is precise, not because the claim is metaphysical. The motebit has an interior the way a droplet has an interior: as a consequence of having a boundary that encloses a volume. The consequence is sufficient without the mysticism.\n\n---",
